Production, imports, exports, and consumption of hardwood timber products, by major product, 1950-87

Dataset containing statistics for hardwood timber products. All units are in million cubic ft.

pietc_hwt

Format

A data frame with 48 observations of 22 variables:

Years

Years

AllProduction.Prod

Total production of all products

AllProduct.Consump

Total consumption of all products

Ind.RW.Tot.Prod

Total production of all industrial roundwood products

Ind.RW.Tot.Imports

Total imports of all industrial roundwood products

Ind.RW.Tot.Exports

Total exports of all industrial roundwood products

Ind.RW.Tot.Consump

Total consumption of all industrial roundwood products

Ind.RW.Lum.Prod

Production of lumber products

Ind.RW.Lum.Imports

Imports of lumber products

Ind.RW.Lum.Exports

Exports of lumber products

Ind.RW.Lum.Consump

Consumption of lumber products

Ind.RW.PlyandVen.Prod

Production of plywood and veneer products

Ind.RW.PlyandVen.Imports

Imports of plywood and veneer products

Ind.RW.PlyandVen.Exports

Exports of plywood and veneer products

Ind.RW.PlyandVen.Consump

Consumption of plywood and veneer products

Ind.RW.Pulp.Prod

Production of pulp products

Ind.RW.Pulp.Imports

Imports of pulp products

Ind.RW.Pulp.Exports

Exports of pulp products

Ind.RW.Pulp.Consump

Consumption of pulp products

Ind.RW.OtherIndustrial.ProdAndConsump

Production and consumption of Other industrial roundwood products

Ind.RW.Logs.Imports

Imports of logs

Ind.RW.Logs.Exports

Exports of logs

FuelWood.ProdAndConsumption

Production and Consumption of Fuelwood

UnNamed1

Unnamed

Source

Based on data published by the U.S. Departments of Commerce and Agriculture.
